                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                                        <placeName>New York</placeName>\n                                        <date>August 30<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi> 1848</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>\n                                        <addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                                        <placeName>Philad</placeName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(2)\">My dear Friend</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(3)\">Your letter of <date>17<hi rend=\"sup\"\n                                                  >th</hi></date> inst was duly<lb/> received and\n                                        contents noticed, since which time I have used<lb/> my\n                                        utmost exertions to procure for you the amt named. But<lb/>\n                                        I must say I have been unsuccessful and know not how to\n                                        get<lb/> it in time for you as my Friends are all short here\n                                        at present.<lb/> and I cannot get the money just now even at\n                                                  <sic>at</sic> a considerable<lb/> sacrifice. But I\n                                        will promise you that if you can get <persName>M\n                                                  Sherman</persName><lb/> to wait a short time. It\n                                        shall not be long before you receive the<lb/> amt. It gives\n                                        me to the very start to think I am compelled<lb/> to\n                                        disappoint <hi rend=\"underline\">you</hi> and many sleepless\n                                        nights have I passed in<lb/> consequence. The reason why I\n                                        did not reply to your letter at once<lb/> was that I wished\n                                        to try <hi rend=\"underline\">all ways</hi> before I could\n                                        give you a decided<lb/> answer. I will now repeat that you\n                                        shall not wait long.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(9)\">In great haste</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(10)\">Yours most truly</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(10)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">W. S. Hanford</persName>\n                              </p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3vd6pm9v/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
